ren:props:items:6\"],\"title\":\"Plushy Companions at a glance\",\"text\":\"Quickly scan type, audience, highlight, rating, and price.\"}]\nb:[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$22\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@23\"}]}]\n24:[]\nc:\"$W24\"\nd:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L25\",null,{\"children\":\"$L26\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L27\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$22\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.Metadata\",\"children\":\"$L28\"}]}]}],null]}]\n29:I[8500,[\"756\",\"static/chunks/756-98a13f2d10827e2b.js\",\"478\",\"static/chunks/478-0efb1bba4c5cfee2.js\",\"624\",\"static/chunks/app/plushy-companions/page-e6fb5a3c20605f42.js\"],\"\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/Percy-1.1-Robotic-Companion-Dog.png\",\"image\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/Joy-for-All-Companion-Cat-Tuxedo.jpg\",\"image\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/Joy-For-All-Golden-Pup.png\",\"image\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/Perfect-Petzzz-Original-Black-and-White-Shorthair-Cat.png\",\"image\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/Mr-Shih-Tzu.png\",\"image\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/Ropet-Kamomo.png\",\"image\"]\n:HL[\"/images/products/red_panda.png\",\"image\"]\n10:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-3xl space-y-5 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"What are plushy companions?\"}],\" \",\"Plushy companions are soft, lifelike pets designed for tactile comfort and gentle interaction rather than complex play. Most respond to touch, sound, or movement with small actions — a purr, a heartbeat, a slow blink, a head turn — that create a sense of presence without the demands of a live pet. They sit somewhere between a stuffed animal and a robotic pet: more responsive than the former, simpler and more approachable than the latter.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Who are plushy companions for?\"}],\" \",\"The category is most often chosen for three situations: an older adult living alone or in memory care who would benefit from quiet companionship, a child who isn’t ready for the responsibility of a live pet, and an adult who wants the comfort of a pet but can’t accommodate one (allergies, lease restrictions, travel, or grief after losing a pet). Plushy companions are also a common gift for these audiences because they require no setup, no app, and no learning curve.\"]}]]}]\n11:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 max-w-3xl rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6 sm:p-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-trust-900 sm:text-2xl\",\"children\":\"What to look for when choosing\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Realism vs. price\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Realism vs. price\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Higher-end plushy companions use more sophisticated mechanics for breathing and movement; budget models are simpler but still effective.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Battery vs. plug-in\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Battery vs. plug-in\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Most run on standard batteries; some premium models charge via dock.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Care and cleaning\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Care and cleaning\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Look for products with removable, washable fur covers if the recipient is in a care setting.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Noise level\",{\"c